---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
        <div class="prose prose-base lg:prose-lg text-base-content max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-primary mb-8">
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8">
                Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
            </p>

            <p>
                At Barq Telecommunication Pvt Ltd., protecting your privacy and
                ensuring the security of your data is a top priority. This
                Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your
                personal information when you use our services.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>
                To provide you with reliable telecommunications and internet
                services, we may collect the following:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, address, email, and phone
                    number provided during registration.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Billing Information:</strong> Payment details, transaction
                    history, and subscription status.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Network Usage Data:</strong> IP addresses, bandwidth consumption,
                    and diagnostic data necessary for network optimization and troubleshooting.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                How We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <p>
                We do not sell your personal data. We use the information we
                collect strictly to:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Deliver, maintain, and improve our fiber and wireless
                    network infrastructure.
                </li>
                <li>Process billing and subscription management.</li>
                <li>Provide customer care and technical support.</li>
                <li>
                    Communicate service updates, outages, or security alerts.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
            <p>
                Barq implements industry-standard security measures, including
                encryption and strict access controls, to protect your personal
                and billing information against unauthorized access, alteration,
                or disclosure.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-base-200 rounded-xl">
                <p class="font-bold m-0">Data Privacy Concerns?</p>
                <p class="text-sm mt-2 mb-0">
                    If you wish to update your data or have questions about our
                    privacy practices, please <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="text-primary hover:underline">contact us</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
